{"tid":1537691,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"晚晚係各區警署/保皇警察宿舍高官屋企/禮賓府外面busking，跳大媽舞，途人就一齊歡呼唱歌","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:46:01.000Z","uid":261343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"839e69a53dae6d71244104d3db05a23d67fc4f5c","tid":1537691,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"人地屯門大媽可以咁做<br />\n黨察又咁幫佢地<br />\n我地學佢地實無問題喇<br />\n你地話玩長期戰？<br />\n我地陪你慢慢玩<br />\n<br />\n納粹政府一錯再錯<br />\n請後果自負<br />\n唔好到時收唔到科就推卸責任<br />\n賴我地太過分<br />\n根本係你地咎由自取<br />\n唔聽我地市民意見既後果<br />\n應該係成班管治團隊自己承擔後果<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好睇少香港人<br />\n平時治安好係我地自律<br />\n唔係因為黨察<br />\n若果真係要去犯法同游走法律<br />\n香港人應該係所有國家入面數一數二<br />\n我相信最後一定係香港人嬴<br />\n只係時間問題同究竟中國同林鄭會犧牲左幾多野<br />\n去換黎最後既屈服<br />\n<br />\n團結就是力量<br />\n這一場不只是革命<br />\n更是一場覺醒<br />\n一場香港民族主義的覺醒<br />\n從來沒有想到有一樣東西是身為香港人而感到驕傲<br />\n但現在有了<br />\n<br />\n我可以十分驕傲地跟其他國家的人說<br />\n我是香港人<br />\n我們十分團結地對抗政府<br />\n和理非和勇武互相補位<br />\n引證香港民族是十分團結和有智慧<br />\n可以說是以人口比例來說民智最高的民族<br />\n<br />\n政府越過份<br />\n只會令更多人由港豬覺醒做香港智人<br />\n香港人只會越團結<br />\n所以我地真係要多謝林鄭團結左我地上下一代<br />\n<br />\n最後請香港政府要記住四隻字<br />\n<br />\n還。政。於。民"},{"pid":"e93bc5afd7f7d8210587327900baa926c13f97a8","tid":1537691,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2498f2c728ea0bbb2de111375c18eb40feb0a45b","tid":1537691,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9e75c2e41f1511f665ab63a5810833a855d067","tid":1537691,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2498f2c728ea0bbb2de111375c18eb40feb0a45b","tid":1537691,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"一齊busking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1d87a31b9ace24ef23f600dd4deddcde5faa64","tid":1537691,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17bb7ef2ad884734bd68360a902efb3080eb9ec0","tid":1537691,"uid":108337,"like"